name: Tunnel Road
description: Experience the thrill of speed in Tunnel Road. Navigate through endless futuristic tunnels, avoid obstacles, and set new high scores in this fast-paced arcade game.

name: 2048 Classic
description: Play the original 2048 Classic puzzle game. Slide tiles to combine matching numbers and reach the 2048 tile. A simple yet addictive brain teaser.

name: Bubble Game 3D
description: Shoot and pop bubbles in a 3D environment with Bubble Game 3D. Match colors, clear the board, and enjoy a modern twist on the classic bubble shooter genre.

name: Merge Flowers
description: Create a beautiful garden in Merge Flowers. Combine identical flowers to discover new species and expand your floral collection in this relaxing game.

name: Weapons and Ragdolls
description: Unleash chaos in Weapons and Ragdolls. Experiment with various weapons on ragdoll physics characters for hilarious and action-packed moments.

name: Arcade Rope
description: Swing through levels like a pro in Arcade Rope. Master the physics of swinging and timing to avoid hazards and reach the finish line.

name: Pizza Tycoon
description: Build your pizza empire in Pizza Tycoon. Manage your pizzeria, serve hungry customers, and upgrade your shop to become the ultimate pizza chef.

name: Egg Adventure 2
description: Join the egg on a new journey in Egg Adventure 2. Solve puzzles, overcome obstacles, and guide the egg to safety in this charming platformer.

name: Obby On a Bike
description: Test your biking skills in Obby On a Bike. Navigate through challenging obstacle courses on your bicycle and prove your parkour mastery.

name: Cat Chaos Simulator
description: Embrace the life of a mischievous cat in Cat Chaos Simulator. Explore, knock things over, and cause mayhem in this fun simulation game.

name: Dynamons 11
description: Catch and train unique creatures in Dynamons 11. Battle other trainers, evolve your Dynamons, and become the greatest captain in this RPG adventure.

name: Aqua Blitz 2
description: Dive into the underwater world of Aqua Blitz 2. Match 3 or more aquatic items to clear levels and unlock treasures in this refreshing puzzle game.

name: Hidden Easter Egg Hunt
description: Search for hidden Easter eggs in various scenes with Hidden Easter Egg Hunt. Sharpen your observation skills and find all the hidden items.

name: Parkour Block 7
description: Jump and climb through blocky worlds in Parkour Block 7. Navigate difficult terrain and reach the portal in this Minecraft-inspired parkour game.

name: Solitaire Mahjong
description: Enjoy a classic game of Solitaire Mahjong. Match pairs of tiles to clear the board and relax with this timeless puzzle game.

name: Uphill Rush 13
description: Race through water parks and roller coasters in Uphill Rush 13. Perform stunts, collect coins, and finish the course as fast as possible.

name: Snow Rush 3D
description: Slide down snowy slopes in Snow Rush 3D. Avoid trees and rocks, collect gifts, and see how far you can go in this winter sports game.

name: Doge's Battle Royale
description: Fight for survival in Doge's Battle Royale. Compete against other Doges, collect weapons, and be the last one standing in this quirky action game.

name: Brick Match
description: Challenge your mind with Brick Match. Fit blocks together to complete lines and score points in this addictive puzzle game.

name: One Line
description: Connect the dots with a single continuous line in One Line. Solve increasingly difficult geometric puzzles to train your brain.

name: Draw Weapon Fight Party
description: Draw your own weapons and fight in Draw Weapon Fight Party. Use creativity to defeat opponents in this unique combat game.

name: Capybara Suika
description: Combine cute animals in Capybara Suika. Drop and merge characters to create the ultimate Capybara in this watermelon-style puzzle game.

name: 2048 Merge Circle
description: A circular twist on the classic 2048. Shoot numbers into a circle and merge them to reach high scores in 2048 Merge Circle.

name: Robby: Bomberman
description: Place bombs and blast enemies in Robby: Bomberman. Strategize your moves to trap opponents and survive in this explosive arcade game.

name: Two Archers: Bow Duel
description: Test your aim in Two Archers: Bow Duel. Compete in archery battles, hit targets, and defeat your rival with precision shots.

name: Zig Snake
description: Guide the snake through a zigzag path in Zig Snake. React quickly to turns, collect food, and grow your snake without falling off.

name: Zen Master - 3 tiles
description: Find peace and match tiles in Zen Master - 3 tiles. A relaxing tile-matching game designed to calm your mind and challenge your focus.

name: Lollipop Stack Run
description: Build delicious lollipop stacks in Lollipop Stack Run. Collect ingredients, avoid obstacles, and serve sweet treats at the finish line.

name: Physics Balls
description: Shoot balls and break bricks in Physics Balls. Utilize physics and angles to clear the screen in this satisfying arcade game.
